    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Hungarian Chamber ([Vienna], 12 November
                    1551)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p>The King has left János Szentpéteri in Likavka to look after the castle
                            for a set period of time, until he orders otherwise, so he recommends
                            him to their attention. He is strapped for cash right now due to having
                            to pay the infantrymen who are stationed in the castle. Oláh is asking
                            them to look after them, so they do not lack anything in the castle.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p>Reverende et Egregii Domini, Amici nobis Honorandissimi, salutem et
                    nostri commendationem!</p>
                <p><persName>Iohannem Zempethery</persName><note type="critic">Probably
                        János Szentpéteri, who was Castellan of Likava. We know two of his letters,
                        dated 15 and 18 August, 1551 in Likava, see <hi rend="smallcap"
                            >Bessenyei</hi> 2013, 248.</note>
                    <persName>maiestas regia</persName> ad certum tempus in arcem
                        <placeName>Lykawa</placeName>,<note type="critic">Likavka.</note> donec de
                    ea arce aliter provideat,<note type="critic">It was necessary due to Lajos
                        Pekry’s death, see Ep. 787.</note><ref>/o:olahus.tei.15511027_1</ref>
                    reliquit, quare ipsum Dominationibus Vestris commendo. Eget autem pecunia pro
                    solutione peditum, quos in arce alit. Oro itaque Dominationes Vestras, ut ei
                    providere velint, ne quis defectus in arce contingat. Easdem bene valere
                    optamus.</p>
                <p>Datum 12. Novembris anno Domini MDLI.</p>
                <p>
                    <seg type="signature"><add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Vester Agriensis etc.
                            manu propria</add></seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p>Reverendo et egregiis dominis consiliariis camerae Hungaricae regiae
                    maiestatis etc. dominis et amicis honorandissimis.</p>
                
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
